CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper November 24, 1956, pg. A10, reads: "Bethel Honors Pastor and Wife - Pausing in the midst of their drive for building a new edifice, members of Bethel AME Church gave a welcome reception for the Rev. and Mrs. C. S. Spivey Jr. Monday evening... - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Spivey accepting envelope from Agatha Fields with Rev. C. S. Spivey Jr. standing between them in Bethel AME Church
